name: kernello/cloudabis-sdk
description: CloudABIS™ can compare millions of ISO fingerprint templates/sec for fast 1:N matching & de-duplication requirements. Customers simply connect through our API or CloudApper™ software & instantly have the ability to perform fast 1:N matching. Our software supports many fingerprint readers & device activation is seamless with our CloudScanr™ app. CloudScanr™ also enables the biometric system to instantly work across any web browser.
